{"id": "pos022", "name": "Audio_Xmas_688_12_24_2", "res": null, "contents": [[{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Bar_HeavenNote"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Dishes", "Collecting Tableware"], "content": ""}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Shop Owner"], "content": "Helena, ten-minute break. Go see your little sister.\nEverybody, hang in there. It's almost over!\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "Got it. Thank you!\nAroma, are you bored?\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "Not at all. When sister is working hard, you look very cool.\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "It's not like I purposely want to look cool though. I'm exhausted~\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "Thanks for the hard work.\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "Since I worked overtime tonight, I don't have a shift tomorrow afternoon. So, what do you want to do? Any place you want to go?\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "Not really. Going out means spending money. It's fine just staying at home with sister.\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "It's a holiday though. We can still go on a walk somewhere, right? You know, to check out the Christmas decorations and such?\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "Hmm... I feel like it will be very crowded no matter where we go. It's a bit scary...\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "Haha, alright. Staying at home it is then.\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Shop Owner"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">What!? You serious?</font>\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Staff A"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">Yes... What should we do...?</font>\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "... What's the matter?\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Shop Owner"], "content": "Our resident singer got caught in a massive traffic jam. She might be late for quite some time...\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "EH!?\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Shop Owner"], "content": "Damnit, we've got so many customers. A lot of them are here for the performance... The Christmas secret event is supposed to be the climax of today's show!\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Staff A"], "content": "The crowd is getting more and more restless...\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Shop Owner"], "content": "All in all, we can't just leave the stage empty like this. Got to figure out a way somehow!\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Staff A"], "content": "......\nDuring the promotion, we didn't specify what the secret event is going to be, did we?\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[»»» Fast Forward »»»]</i>\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "... Eh? Me?\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Shop Owner"], "content": "Please! Aroma's singing is great. 15 min... No! 10! Just stand-in for 10 minutes and we'll be fine!\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "Owner, this child is extremely shy. Telling her to sing on stage is...\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Shop Owner"], "content": "I know! But...... Ah! Right! This, wear this to cover up your face. This way, nobody will know who you are! All you need to do is close your eyes and focus on your singing!\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "Owner!\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "... I'll try. \n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "Eh?\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "Sir treated me to some orange juice. I want to help...\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "Aroma......\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[»»» Fast Forward »»»]</i>\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Customer A"], "content": "Why hasn't anything started! Where is the show?\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Customer B"], "content": "Yeah! I want a refund, old man! Haha!\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Shop Owner"], "content": "Shut your pie holes! Hmph, you guys are going to see the best show ever right now, let me tell you.\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["WinterGames_Preview", "Music"], "content": ""}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Customer C"], "content": "Eh? A child?\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Customer D"], "content": "Hey! We want to see a sexy lady~ When has this place become an art class for kids?\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "<i>*All the store lights\nShining so bright\nWarm the chill in the air\nThrough their doors stream melodies of winter*</i>\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Audience"], "content": "......!\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[»»» Fast Forward »»»]</i>\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "...... (Bows)\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Audience_02", "Audience Cheers"], "content": ""}, {"id": 43, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[»»» Fast Forward »»»]</i>\n"}, {"id": 44, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Customer A"], "content": "Wow~ Tonight's show was incredible!\n"}, {"id": 45, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Customer B"], "content": "Especially that opening with the little girl wearing a mask! Her voice is beautiful... I wonder who she is?\n"}, {"id": 46, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Staff A"], "content": "Thank you for coming!\n"}, {"id": 47, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Shop Owner"], "content": "Thank you so much for the help today. You can leave now. We'll handle the cleanup afterward.\n"}, {"id": 48, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "Thank you. Good work, everyone.\n"}, {"id": 49, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Shop Owner"], "content": "Aroma, thanks a lot for today! Come visit us again someday.\n"}, {"id": 50, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "Ok!\n"}, {"id": 51, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "In the end, I wasn't able to spend Christmas with you... sorry.\n"}, {"id": 52, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "I don't mind... I feel like I already experience a wonderful Christmas. Thank you, sister.\n"}, {"id": 53, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "Good to hear that~ Aroma, Merry Christmas.\n"}, {"id": 54, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "Yes... Merry Christmas.\n"}, {"id": 55, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[Signal Lost]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Bar_HeavenNote"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Dishes", "食器を片付ける"], "content": ""}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["店長"], "content": "Helena、10分休憩！Aromaちゃんのところに行ってあげるんだ。\nみんな！あと少しだ！頑張れ！\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "はい、ありがとうございます！\nAroma、つまらなくない？\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "全然。\nお姉ちゃんの一生懸命仕事してるところ、すごくかっこいい。\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "カッコつけてるわけじゃないんだけどな～\n疲れた～\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "お疲れ様。\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "今日残業したから、明日のシフトなくなったの。\nどこか出かけようか。\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "大丈夫だよ。\n出かけたらお金かかるでしょ？\nお姉ちゃんと一緒なら、お家でも楽しいよ。\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "でも、せっかくの休みなんだし、少し出かけない？\nクリスマスのイルミネーション見たり。ね？\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "うん……でも、どこもかしこも人だらけで、少し怖いなって……\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "あはは、分かった。\nじゃあ、家でのんびりしよっか。\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["店長"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">なに！？本当か！？</font>\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["店員 A"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">はい……どうしましょう……？</font>\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "……どうしたんですか？\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["店長"], "content": "今日ステージに立つ予定の歌手が渋滞に巻き込まれて、しばらく来れそうにないらしいんだ……\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "ええ！？\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["店長"], "content": "ああ！なんてことだ！\n客はみんな今日のステージを見に来たってのに……クリスマスシークレットイベントは今日の目玉だぞ！\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["店員 A"], "content": "皆さんもざわつき始めました……\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["店長"], "content": "ステージをこのまま誰もいない状態にするわけにはいかない！\n何か方法を考えないと！\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["店員 A"], "content": "………\nシークレットイベントの内容は公開してませんよね？\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[»»»早送り»»»]</i>\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "……え？私？\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["店長"], "content": "お願いだAromaちゃん！\nAromaちゃんは歌も上手だし！\n15分……いや、10分でいい！\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "店長、この子は人見知りなんです。\nステージで歌うなんて……\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["店長"], "content": "分かってる！でも……そうだ！\nこれで顔を隠せばいい！\nそうすれば、誰も君が誰かなんて分からない！\nAromaちゃんは目をつむって歌うだけでいい！\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "店長！\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "……やってみる。\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "え？\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "おじさん、オレンジジュースごちそうしてくれたから。\n私お手伝いしたい……\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "Aroma……\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[»»»早送り»»»]</i>\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["客 A"], "content": "なんでまだ始まらないんだ？\nショーはどうした？\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["客 B"], "content": "そうよ！チケット代返してちょうだい！ははは！\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["店長"], "content": "そんなに慌てないでくださいよ～\nふふふ……\n素晴らしいショーをご覧いただけますよ。\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["WinterGames_Preview", "音楽"], "content": ""}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["客 C"], "content": "はぁ？子供？\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["客 D"], "content": "おーいー！\n俺らはセクシーなお姉さんが見たいんだって！\nここはアーティスト育成学校じゃないんだぞ！\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "<i>*All the store lights\nShining so bright\nWarm the chill in the air\nThrough their doors stream melodies of winter*</i>\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["客"], "content": "……！\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[»»»早送り»»»]</i>\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "……（おじぎ）\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Audience_02", "観客の歓声"], "content": ""}, {"id": 43, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[»»»早送り»»»]</i>\n"}, {"id": 44, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["客 A"], "content": "今日のショーは最高だった！\n"}, {"id": 45, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["客 B"], "content": "特にあの仮面の女の子！\nきれいな歌声だったなぁ～……誰なんだろう？\n"}, {"id": 46, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["店員 A"], "content": "ありがとうございました！\n"}, {"id": 47, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["店長"], "content": "今日は本当にありがとう。\nもうあがっていいぞ。\n後片付けはこっちでやるから。\n"}, {"id": 48, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "ありがとうございます。\nお先に失礼します。\n"}, {"id": 49, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["店長"], "content": "Aromaちゃん！今日はありがとう！\nまたおいでね。\n"}, {"id": 50, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "はい！\n"}, {"id": 51, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "クリスマス一緒に過ごせなかったね……ごめんね。\n"}, {"id": 52, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "いいの……特別なクリスマスになったよ。\nお姉ちゃん、ありがとう。\n"}, {"id": 53, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "ならよかった！\nAroma、メリークリスマス。\n"}, {"id": 54, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "うん……メリークリスマス。\n"}, {"id": 55, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[電波切断]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Bar_HeavenNote"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Dishes", "收拾碗盤"], "content": ""}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["店長"], "content": "Helena，休息十分鐘，去陪妹妹吧。\n大家加油，快結束了！\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "好，謝謝！\nAroma，會無聊嗎？\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "不會，姊姊認真工作的樣子很帥氣。\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "才不是在耍帥呢，快累死了～\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "辛苦了。\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "因為今晚加班，明天下午我不用上班喔，如何？要不要去哪裡晃晃？\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "不用了，出門要花錢。跟姊姊待在家裡也很好。\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "難得假日，還是可以去哪裡散散步吧？看看聖誕節的裝飾之類的？\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "嗯……總覺得到處人都會很多，有點可怕……\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "哈哈，好吧，那就待在家裡吧。\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["店長"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">什麼！？真的嗎？</font>\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["店員 A"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">對……怎麼辦……？</font>\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "……怎麼了？\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["店長"], "content": "駐唱歌手遇到超級塞車，可能會遲到很久……\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "咦！？\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["店長"], "content": "可惡，客人那麼多，大家都是為了看這個來的……聖誕節的神秘活動可是今天的大秀啊！\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["店員 A"], "content": "大家越來越鼓噪了……\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["店長"], "content": "總之不能讓舞台就這樣空著，得想點辦法！\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["店員 A"], "content": "……。\n宣傳的時候沒有說神秘活動的內容會是什麼對吧？\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[»»»快轉»»»]</i>\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "……咦？我？\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["店長"], "content": "拜託了！Aroma 的歌聲很棒的，至少幫忙撐個十五……不！十分鐘就好了！\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "店長，這孩子很怕生的，要她上台唱歌……\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["店長"], "content": "我知道！但是……啊！對了！這個，穿上這個遮住臉，這樣大家都不知道妳是誰了！妳只要閉著眼睛好好唱就行了！\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "店長！\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "……我試試看。\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "咦？\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "叔叔請我喝了果汁了，我想幫忙……\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "Aroma……\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[»»»快轉»»»]</i>\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["客人 A"], "content": "怎麼還沒開始啊？說好的秀呢？\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["客人 B"], "content": "對啊！退票啦大叔！哈哈！\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["店長"], "content": "急屁啊？哼哼，你們馬上會看到最棒的秀我告訴你們。\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["WinterGames_Preview", "音樂"], "content": ""}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["客人 C"], "content": "咦？小孩子？\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["客人 D"], "content": "喂！我們要看性感的大姊姊啦～這裡什麼時候變成才藝班了？\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "<i>*All the store lights\nShining so bright\nWarm the chill in the air\nThrough their doors stream melodies of winter*</i>\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["眾人"], "content": "……！\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[»»»快轉»»»]</i>\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "……（鞠躬）\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Audience_02", "觀眾歡呼"], "content": ""}, {"id": 43, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[»»»快轉»»»]</i>\n"}, {"id": 44, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["客人 A"], "content": "哇～今晚的秀真的太棒了！\n"}, {"id": 45, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["客人 B"], "content": "尤其是開場那個帶面具的小女孩，歌聲好美啊……不知道她是誰？\n"}, {"id": 46, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["店員 A"], "content": "謝謝光臨！\n"}, {"id": 47, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["店長"], "content": "今天真的謝謝妳們了。妳可以下班了，後面的我們來收拾就好。\n"}, {"id": 48, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "謝謝，辛苦大家了。\n"}, {"id": 49, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["店長"], "content": "Aroma，今天謝謝妳啊！有空再來玩吧。\n"}, {"id": 50, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "嗯！\n"}, {"id": 51, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "結果沒有陪妳過到聖誕節……對不起。\n"}, {"id": 52, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "不會……我覺得已經過了很棒的聖誕節了，謝謝姊姊。\n"}, {"id": 53, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "那就好～Aroma，聖誕快樂。\n"}, {"id": 54, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "嗯……聖誕快樂。\n"}, {"id": 55, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[訊號中斷]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Bar_HeavenNote"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Dishes", "그릇을 치운다"], "content": ""}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["점장"], "content": "Helena, 10분간 휴식이다! 가서 동생이랑 같이 좀 있어줘. 자, 모두들. 얼마 안 남았다! 조금만 더 힘내자!\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "네! 감사합니다!\nAroma, 엄청 지루하지?\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "전혀.\n언니가 일하고 있는 모습 보고 있었어. 언니 열심히 일하는 모습, 진짜 멋있는 것 같아.\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "멋있기는 무슨...\n피곤해 죽겠어~\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "고생했어.\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "오늘 추가 근무했기 때문에, 내일 오후에는 출근 안 해도 돼. 내일 어디 같이 갈까? 어때?\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "괜찮아.\n어디 나가면 또 돈 들잖아.\n집에서 놀아도 괜찮아. 언니만 옆에 있으면.\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "그래도 모처럼 휴일인데, 같이 나가서 산책도 하고 그럼 좋잖아? 같이 크리스마스트리 같은 것도 구경하고.\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "음...바깥에 사람들이 너무 많으니깐...조금 무서워...\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "하하하, 알았어. 그럼 집에서 같이 있자.\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["점장"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">뭐!? 그게 정말이야?</font>\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["점원 A"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">네……어떡하죠……？</font>\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "……무슨 일이에요?\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["점장"], "content": "오늘 게스트 가수가 차가 너무 막혀서 엄청 늦을 거라고 하더구나...\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "네!?\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["점장"], "content": "아아아! 많은 손님들이 공연을 보러 온 것일 텐데... 그 가수가 참여한 크리스마스 게릴라 이벤트가 오늘 레스토랑의 클라이맥스였다고!\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["점원 A"], "content": "사람들이 웅성거리기 시작했어요……\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["점장"], "content": "계속 무대를 공백으로 비워둘 순 없어! 빨리 방법을 생각해내야...!\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["점원 A"], "content": "……\n그래도 저희가 한참 홍보했을 때, 게릴라 이벤트의 게스트가 누군지는 공개하지 않았잖아요?\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[»»»빨리 감기»»»]</i>\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "……에? 제가요?\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["점장"], "content": "이렇게 부탁한다! Aroma, 네 목소리도 엄청 좋은 편이니깐 제발 딱 15분만...아니! 10분만이라도 좀 도와주렴!\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "점장님! 제 동생이 낯을 좀 많이 가려요.\n만약 무대에 올라가게 되면...\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["점장"], "content": "나도 알아! 하지만 이대로는....그렇지! 이걸로 얼굴을 가리고 올라가면 저 사람들도 이 아이가 누군지 못 알아볼 거 아니야! Aroma, 이걸 쓰고 그냥 편하게 눈을 감고 노래를 불러주기만 하면 된단다!\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "점장님!\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "……해볼게요.\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "뭐?\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "아저씨가 오렌지 주스를 서비스로 주셨으니깐...나도 뭔가를 해드려야...\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "Aroma……\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[»»»빨리 감기»»»]</i>\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["손님 A"], "content": "대체 언제 시작하는 거야? \n오늘 메인이벤트라던 쇼는?\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["손님 B"], "content": "맞아! 이렇게 된 바에 그냥 전부다 환불해버리라고 형씨! 하하하하!\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["점장"], "content": "보채기는... 에헴! 여러분! 오래 기다리셨습니다! 이제 아주 멋진 공연을 감상하실 시간입니다!\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["WinterGames_Preview", "음악"], "content": ""}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["손님 C"], "content": "엥? 꼬맹이?\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["손님 D"], "content": "어이! 우린 쭉쭉 빵빵의 멋진 누님을 보러 온 거라고! 여긴 대체 언제부터 이런 어린애가 출연하는 재롱잔치 장소가 돼버린 거야!?\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "<i>*All the store lights\nShining so bright\nWarm the chill in the air\nThrough their doors stream melodies of winter*</i>\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["사람들"], "content": "……！\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[»»»빨리 감기»»»]</i>\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "……（허리를 굽혀 인사）\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Audience_02", "관중들의 환호"], "content": ""}, {"id": 43, "type": "text", "att